title: Remove all files to get empty directory
body:
This is necessary to make sure that the publishing bot does not encounter any conflicts while syncing with
staging.

Ref: https://github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/tree/master/staging#creating-the-published-repository

Related: https://github.com/kubernetes/publishing-bot/pull/118

/cc @sttts @spiffxp @yliaog
